001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import com.google.common.base.Preconditions;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007import java.math.BigInteger;
008
009@HistoryLogProps(
010    opCode = 60,
011    displayName = "Data Log Corruption",
012    usedByTidepool = true
013)
014public class DataLogCorruptionHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
015    
016    
017    public DataLogCorruptionHistoryLog() {}
018    public DataLogCorruptionHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum) {
019        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
020        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
021        
022    }
023
024    public int typeId() {
025        return 60;
026    }
027
028    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
029        Preconditions.checkArgument(raw.length == 26);
030        this.cargo = raw;
031        parseBase(raw);
032        
033    }
034
035    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum) {
036        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
037            new byte[]{60, 0},
038            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
039            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum)));
040    }
041    
042}
